<scriptment id="76000" point="dan_home" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-10-24" status="final">
	<part>
	    <comment>Sporadic event for any day between 2011-10-24 and 2011-10-25.</comment>
	    <narration>Yuki, dampened locks and head in cover by coat, passes Dan. Dan sits.</narration>
	    <line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Dan, go home.</line>
	    <narration>Dan sits.</narration>
	    <line id="2000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Dan, go home!</line>
	    <narration>Dan sits. He raises his brow. He shrugs. Yuki gapes.</narration>
	    <line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">They didn't.</line>
	    <line id="4000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">They sure did.</line>
	    <line id="4100" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">Airlines are expensive. Shelter is too.</line>
	    <narration>An airplane flies overhead.</narration>
	    <line id="5000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Is it out of the question to move in with your parents?</line>
	    <line id="6000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">My family lives in America.</line>
	    <condition>
	        <choice number="1">
	            <line id="7000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">That's too bad.</line>
	            <line id="8000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I hope you can find a roommate.</line>
	            <narration>Dan stares down his feet. Yuki pats him on the shoulder.</narration>
	            <line id="9000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I'm sorry! We have not room for another in our house.</line>
	            <line id="10000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I'm newly married&#x2014;</line>
	            <line id="11000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">Are you?</line>
	            <narration>Yuki sulks.</narration>
	        </choice>
	        <choice number="2">
	            <line id="12000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">I could lend you some cash.</line>
	            <line id="13000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">You could lend me some cash!</line>
	            <line id="14000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Straight from the corporate account.</line>
	            <line id="15000" speaker="dan" voicelang="ja">Straight from the corporate account!</line>
	            <line id="16000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="ja">Just don't waste it on frivolous things like water.</line>
	            <narration>Yuki does some online banking. <comment>The Player loses 160,000 Yen.</comment></narration>
	        </choice>
        </condition>
    </part>
</scriptment>
